TO KNOW TO CONVICT HIM

26:26.418 --> 26:29.722
OF HIS CRIMES.

26:35.928 --> 26:39.732
- WHAT AM I THINKING
RIGHT NOW?

26:39.766 --> 26:41.367
THAT I WISH I'D HAD
A SECOND CUP OF COFFEE

26:41.400 --> 26:43.670
BEFORE COURT THIS MORNING,

26:43.703 --> 26:46.739
OR THAT MR. BARBA'S
PROSECUTION IS SO WRONG

26:46.773 --> 26:48.741
THAT HE SHOULD
BE TAKEN OUT AND SHOT?

26:52.912 --> 26:54.747
YOU CAN'T TELL, CAN YOU?

26:54.781 --> 26:56.716
AND WHAT DOES IT MATTER?

26:56.749 --> 26:57.950
DO I DESERVE TO BE PUNISHED
FOR SOMETHING

26:57.984 --> 26:59.752
THAT'S ONLY
INSIDE MY HEAD?

26:59.786 --> 27:01.320
- OBJECTION.
MS. EFRON IS ARGUING THE WISDOM

27:01.353 --> 27:03.222
OF THE LAW AND NOT
MAKING AN OPENING STATEMENT.

27:03.255 --> 27:06.158
- MS. EFRON, WATCH YOURSELF.
- I'M SORRY, YOUR HONOR.

27:06.192 --> 27:08.227
