BEATEN, AND ROBBED?

31:16.608 --> 31:18.144
- OBJECTION.

31:18.177 --> 31:19.645
WHAT'S THE QUESTION?

31:19.678 --> 31:21.547
- SUSTAINED.

31:21.580 --> 31:25.417
- YOUR SEXUAL BEHAVIOR DOES
INCLUDE VIOLENCE, DOESN'T IT?

31:25.451 --> 31:27.119
- NO.

31:27.153 --> 31:28.320
WHEN I'M WITH MY HUSBAND,
WE TAKE THINGS EASY.

31:28.354 --> 31:29.621
SLOW AND EASY.

31:29.655 --> 31:32.691
- BUT WHEN YOU CRUISE,
YOU ONLY FIND PARTNERS

31:32.724 --> 31:36.295
WHO LIKE THINGS
HARD AND FAST.

31:36.328 --> 31:37.529
WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

31:37.563 --> 31:38.630
- WELL, IT'S LIKE I SAID.

31:38.664 --> 31:41.500
MEN LIKE THAT,
THEY LIKE TO PLAY ROUGH.

31:41.533 --> 31:44.470
- "MEN LIKE THAT."

31:44.503 --> 31:47.039
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

31:47.073 --> 31:50.509
- YOU SAW THEM.
THEY'RE TRYING TO LOOK STRAIGHT.

31:50.542 --> 31:52.511
- YOU HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

31:52.544 --> 31:56.615
- ONLY THAT IT'S NOT HONEST.
LOOK, I DON'T HIDE WHAT I AM.

31:56.648 --> 31:59.485
I'M GLAD THAT I'M GAY.
I'M PROUD TO BE GAY.

31:59.518 --> 32:01.287
- AS MUCH AS TIMES HAVE CHANGED,

32:01.320 --> 32:03.489
IT STILL TAKES COURAGE
TO COME OUT, DOESN'T IT?

32:03.522 --> 32:05.057
- YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT.

32:05.091 --> 32:08.394
- SO THOSE MEN,
THEY'RE GAY WHEN IT'S FUN,

32:08.427 --> 32:11.130
