32:11.163 --> 32:13.565
DOES THAT SEEM FAIR TO YOU?
- DOES IT SEEM FAIR TO YOU?

32:13.599 --> 32:15.334
- HM.

32:15.367 --> 32:17.703
DO YOU EVER THINK YOUR LIFE
WOULD BE EASIER

32:17.736 --> 32:19.571
IF YOU COULD
PASS FOR STRAIGHT?

