I AM WHAT I AM.

32:22.374 --> 32:27.113
- BUT THOSE MEN--THE ONES
WHO CAN PASS FOR STRAIGHT.

32:27.146 --> 32:29.581
THE ONES
WHO AREN'T EFFEMINATE.

32:29.615 --> 32:32.084
