DON'T YOU?

32:32.118 --> 32:33.585
- NO. NOT ESPECIALLY.

32:33.619 --> 32:35.554
- THEY'RE THE ONES YOU SERVICE,
AREN'T THEY?

32:35.587 --> 32:37.656
- NO. NO, I DON'T.
- YOU TAKE THEM TO HOTELS.

32:37.689 --> 32:39.658
WHAT DO THEY ASK YOU TO DO
ONCE YOU GET THERE?

32:39.691 --> 32:41.360
- THAT DOESN'T MATTER.
- WHY NOT?

32:41.393 --> 32:42.728
BECAUSE YOU TAKE CHARGE?
- [chuckles]

32:42.761 --> 32:45.297
OKAY, I DON'T GET DOWN
ON MY KNEES FOR THEM,

32:45.331 --> 32:46.598
IF THAT'S WHAT--

32:46.632 --> 32:47.666
- IS THAT WHAT
THEY ASK YOU TO DO?

32:47.699 --> 32:49.268
- IT DOESN'T MATTER.
- WHY?

32:49.301 --> 32:50.469
THEY'RE THE ONES
WHO ARE SUCCESSFUL.

32:50.502 --> 32:51.537
THEY'RE THE ONES
WITH THE MONEY.

32:51.570 --> 32:53.305
THE ONES WHO
MOVE BETWEEN WORLDS.

32:53.339 --> 32:54.406
- YEAH, IS THAT SUPPOSED
TO IMPRESS ME OR SOMETHING?

32:54.440 --> 32:55.441
- I DON'T KNOW, YOU TELL ME.

32:55.474 --> 32:56.575
CONSIDERING YOU'RE--WHAT?

32:56.608 --> 32:59.678
A PART-TIME UNEMPLOYED
MALE STRIPPER.

32:59.711 --> 33:01.680
WHAT DO THEY SAY TO YOU?
WHAT DO THEY ASK YOU TO DO?

33:01.713 --> 33:04.016
- IT DOESN'T MATTER!

33:09.088 --> 33:12.691
OKAY, YOU KNOW,
THEY MAY HAVE THEIR FAKE WIVES

33:12.724 --> 33:16.395
