33:23.602 --> 33:27.473
THE LIES ARE OVER!

33:27.506 --> 33:31.143
I AM JUST AS MUCH
A MAN AS THEY ARE.

33:31.177 --> 33:34.213
MORE.

33:45.091 --> 33:47.659
- YOUR HONOR,
COULD WE SPEAK IN CHAMBERS?

33:59.771 --> 34:01.207
- WE ALL JUST HEARD
MR. BARBA DISPROVE HIS CASE.

34:01.240 --> 34:02.308
- EXCUSE ME?

34:02.341 --> 34:04.710
- YOU GOT JONES
TO LET HIS GUARD DOWN.

34:04.743 --> 34:06.412
IT WAS BRILLIANT.

34:06.445 --> 34:08.480
YOU GOT HIM TO REALLY
TELL YOU HOW HE FEELS.

34:08.514 --> 34:10.349
- EXACTLY.

34:10.382 --> 34:11.750
HE HATES THE PEOPLE HE ATTACKED
BECAUSE OF WHO THEY ARE.

34:11.783 --> 34:13.719
HE BASICALLY CONFESSED
TO COMMITTING A HATE CRIME.

34:13.752 --> 34:15.321
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I HEARD.

34:15.354 --> 34:17.556
I HEARD A CLEAR DISPLAY
OF ANIMUS,

34:17.589 --> 34:20.292
NOT AGAINST GAY MEN,
BUT AGAINST A SUBSET--

34:20.326 --> 34:23.262
CLOSETED GAY MEN
WHO CAN PASS AS STRAIGHT.

34:23.295 --> 34:25.831
- A DISTINCTION
WITHOUT A DIFFERENCE.

34:25.864 --> 34:27.566
- OOH, IT'S
A CRUCIAL DIFFERENCE.

34:27.599 --> 34:29.401
IF I GO OUT AND BEAT UP JEWS,
THAT'S A HATE CRIME.

34:29.435 --> 34:32.338
IF I BEAT UP LEFT-HANDED JEWS,
THAT'S ASSAULT.

34:32.371 --> 34:34.740
I MOVE FOR DISMISSAL
OF THE HATE CRIME CHARGE.

34:34.773 --> 34:36.175
- SHE'S SPLITTING HAIRS
THAT COULDN'T BE SEEN

34:36.208 --> 34:37.409
WITH AN ELECTRON MICROSCOPE.

34:37.443 --> 34:38.877
- I'M NOT SO SURE,
MR. BARBA.

34:38.910 --> 34:40.846
IT DOES SEEM LIKE
A BIT OF AN OVERREACH.

34:40.879 --> 34:43.249
- THE STATUTE IS CLEAR.

34:43.282 --> 34:45.484
- BUT YOUR CASE ISN'T.

34:45.517 --> 34:47.153
I KNOW THAT YOU BOTH AGREE

34:47.186 --> 34:49.388
HOW IMPORTANT
THE HATE CRIME STATUTE IS.

34:49.421 --> 34:51.623
