TO SEE IT TRIVIALIZED

34:51.657 --> 34:53.759
BY INDISCRIMINATE USE.

34:53.792 --> 34:55.561
- ALL DUE RESPECT,
ISN'T IT UP TO THE JURY

34:55.594 --> 34:57.329
TO DECIDE IF IT APPLIES?

34:57.363 --> 35:01.433
- HOLD ON, DENNIS.

35:01.467 --> 35:04.670
