OF WHAT HE GOT TO HIS HUSBAND,

37:22.073 --> 37:23.342
LIKE THE WATCH
THAT MASON WAS WEARING.

37:23.375 --> 37:24.676
- YOU CHECKED THAT OUT.

37:24.710 --> 37:25.944
IT DIDN'T BELONG
TO ANY KNOWN VICTIM.

37:25.977 --> 37:27.546
- SLOW DOWN, COUNSELOR.

37:27.579 --> 37:29.648
ON THE STAND, JONES
TALKED ABOUT THE MEN HE HATES

37:29.681 --> 37:33.719
BUYING ANNIVERSARY GIFTS
FOR THEIR FAKE WIVES.

37:33.752 --> 37:35.954
IT'S A FUNNY IDEA
TO POP INTO HIS HEAD.

37:35.987 --> 37:39.525
- LAUREL DUNLEAVY TOLD US
THAT HER HUSBAND DIED

37:39.558 --> 37:42.294
A FEW DAYS
BEFORE THEIR ANNIVERSARY.

37:42.328 --> 37:45.431
- SO IF HE BOUGHT HER SOMETHING
AND HE HAD IT WITH HIM

37:45.464 --> 37:46.665
WHEN JONES KILLED HIM--

37:46.698 --> 37:48.033
- JONES TOOK IT.

37:48.066 --> 37:49.735
THERE WAS NOTHING
IN THAT HOTEL ROOM.

37:49.768 --> 37:53.505
AND THAT SHOULD TIE HIM
TO THE MURDER VICTIM.

37:53.539 --> 37:54.906
- RUN DUNLEAVY'S
CREDIT CARDS.

37:54.940 --> 37:56.842
SEE IF HE DID ANY
ANNIVERSARY SHOPPING

37:56.875 --> 37:59.411
ON THE DAY
HE WAS KILLED.

37:59.445 --> 38:00.579
- I KNOW MY RIGHTS, OKAY?

38:00.612 --> 38:02.414
I DON'T HAVE
TO TALK TO ANY OF YOU.

38:02.448 --> 38:04.383
- THAT'S WHY WE APPRECIATE
YOUR VOLUNTARY COOPERATION.

38:04.416 --> 38:05.817
- YEAH, YOU SAID
IF I DIDN'T COME,

38:05.851 --> 38:07.319
YOU'D ARREST ME AGAIN.

38:07.353 --> 38:09.588
- I MISSPOKE.
YOUR WITNESS.

38:09.621 --> 38:13.492
- COME WITH US, MASON,
THIS WON'T TAKE LONG.

38:13.525 --> 38:15.394
- I DON'T WANT
TO DO THIS ANYMORE, OKAY?

38:15.427 --> 38:16.828
MY WHOLE LIFE
IS UPSIDE DOWN.

38:16.862 --> 38:18.530
- I JUST HAVE
ONE SIMPLE QUESTION.

38:18.564 --> 38:20.866
YOU TOLD US THAT JEREMY
GIVES YOU JEWELRY SOMETIMES,

38:20.899 --> 38:22.434
LIKE THE WATCH
THAT YOU SHOWED US.

38:22.468 --> 38:25.537
DID HE GIVE YOU
A PLATINUM BRACELET, TOO?

38:25.571 --> 38:26.905
- NO.

38:26.938 --> 38:28.574
- DID HE GIVE IT TO YOU
THE NIGHT DUNLEAVY WAS MURDERED?

38:28.607 --> 38:30.609
THE NIGHT YOU SAID
JEREMY CAME HOME ALL UPSET.

38:30.642 --> 38:33.445
- I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT THIS ANYMORE.

38:33.479 --> 38:36.582
I CAN'T TESTIFY ANYWAY.
I CAN'T TELL YOU WHAT HE SAID.

38:36.615 --> 38:38.517
- BUT YOU CAN TELL US
WHERE THE BRACELET IS.

38:38.550 --> 38:40.051
- WHAT BRACELET?

38:40.085 --> 38:42.488
- LOOK, HERE'S
THE BILL OF SALE, ALL RIGHT?

38:42.521 --> 38:44.990
DUNLEAVY BOUGHT IT
FOR HIS WIFE THAT AFTERNOON,

38:45.023 --> 38:46.925
FOR THEIR ANNIVERSARY.

38:46.958 --> 38:49.428
NOW, HE DIDN'T TAKE IT HOME
AND IT WASN'T WITH HIS BODY.

38:49.461 --> 38:52.731
- AN I.D. BRACELET?
YOU SEE THOSE ANYWHERE.

38:52.764 --> 38:55.066
- YEAH, LOOK WHAT IT SAYS.
THIS ONE WAS ENGRAVED.

38:55.100 --> 38:56.668
"LOVE YOU MADLY."

39:04.743 --> 39:08.480
- THAT CAN'T BE RIGHT.

39:08.514 --> 39:12.518
- WELL, IT'S RIGHT THERE, MASON.
IT'S BLACK AND WHITE.

39:14.119 --> 39:16.455
- HE TOLD YOU THAT HE BOUGHT IT
FOR YOU, DIDN'T HE?

39:18.424 --> 39:20.726
HE DIDN'T TELL YOU
THAT HE TOOK IT

39:20.759 --> 39:23.762
FROM A MAN THAT HE KILLED.

39:23.795 --> 39:27.566
THAT INSCRIPTION
WASN'T FOR YOU, MASON.

39:27.599 --> 39:29.535
IT WAS FOR
THAT MAN'S WIFE.

39:29.568 --> 39:32.738
- I WANT TO GO RIGHT NOW.

39:32.771 --> 39:34.573
- NOT YET.

39:38.644 --> 39:42.481
- MASON,
THIS IS MRS. DUNLEAVY,

39:42.514 --> 39:46.117
MR. DUNLEAVY'S WIDOW.

39:46.151 --> 39:49.655
- MRS. DUNLEAVY,
I'M SO SORRY.

39:52.458 --> 39:56.962
- YOUR HUSBAND
RAPED MY HUSBAND.

39:56.995 --> 40:01.132
IT'S SUCH AN ODD THING TO SAY,
ISN'T IT?

40:01.166 --> 40:06.104
THEY WERE CHEATING,
WEREN'T THEY?

40:06.137 --> 40:08.940
THEY WERE CHEATING ON US--

40:08.974 --> 40:11.176
YOU AND ME.

40:14.513 --> 40:17.015
BUT HE DIDN'T
HAVE TO KILL HIM.

40:20.886 --> 40:23.522
WHY DID HE KILL HIM?

40:31.229 --> 40:34.833
- WHERE'S THE BRACELET,
MASON?

40:42.574 --> 40:45.143
- I SUGGEST NOMINAL BAIL,
PENDING SENTENCING,

40:45.176 --> 40:47.145
OF, SAY, $5,000.

40:47.178 --> 40:50.181
- MR. BARBA?

40:50.215 --> 40:52.217
- FINE WITH ME, JUDGE.

40:52.250 --> 40:53.685
- REALLY?

40:53.719 --> 40:55.186
- IN THAT CASE,
BAIL IS SET AT 5,000,

40:55.220 --> 40:56.655
CASH OR BOND.

40:56.688 --> 40:58.990
[gavel pounds]

40:59.024 --> 41:01.493
- NO HARD FEELINGS, DETECTIVES.
I'LL SEE YOU ON EIGHTH AVENUE.

41:01.527 --> 41:04.496
- WELL, WE'RE GONNA HAVE
TO POSTPONE THAT FOR A WHILE.

41:04.530 --> 41:06.264
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST
FOR MURDER, MR. JONES.

41:06.297 --> 41:08.667
- [chuckles]
SORE LOSERS, ARE WE?

41:08.700 --> 41:11.737
- THE BRACELET DUNLEAVY
BOUGHT THE DAY HE DIED.

41:13.939 --> 41:17.208
- HIS BLOOD.
YOUR FINGERPRINTS.

41:21.212 --> 41:23.782
- MASON, WHAT DID YOU DO?
- JEREMY, I'M SO SORRY.

41:23.815 --> 41:25.216
- YOU SCARED LITTLE FAGGOT!

41:25.250 --> 41:27.218
- ALL RIGHT, TAKE--JEREMY.
TAKE IT EASY, JEREMY.

41:27.252 --> 41:28.887
- TAKE IT EASY?
OH, I SEE.

41:28.920 --> 41:30.221
YOU'RE IN ON THIS TOO,
AREN'T YOU?

41:30.255 --> 41:32.223
YOU BACKSTABBING BITCH!
- WHAT?

41:32.257 --> 41:34.760
- YOU'RE MY LAWYER, NOT HIS.
YOU THINK YOU CAN SELL ME OUT?

41:34.793 --> 41:36.294
I WILL TAKE
YOU DOWN SO FAST--

41:36.327 --> 41:38.163
- HEY, HEY!
BACK UP, MR. JONES!

41:46.004 --> 41:48.273
- YOU OKAY, COUNSELOR?
- YEAH.

41:48.306 --> 41:51.076
YEAH, I'VE HAD WORSE.
RIGHT?

41:53.679 --> 41:56.181
YOU WERE WRONG ABOUT HIM.
HE DOESN'T JUST HATE GAYS.

41:56.214 --> 41:57.783
- HE HATES EVERYONE.

41:57.816 --> 42:00.819
- NO. HE HATES HIMSELF.
